test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 0 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bd32fc70740>([-51])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bd32fc70740> = [[-51, 1], [-51, 1, -51], [-51], [-51, 1], [-51, 1], [-51, 1, -51], ...].count
 +  and   0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bd32fc70740>([1, -51])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bd32fc70740> = [[-51, 1], [-51, 1, -51], [-51], [-51, 1], [-51, 1], [-51, 1, -51], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -153 == -51
 +  where -153 = <built-in function prod>([-51, -1, -3])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
